瑞玲\r\n本件證明與原本無異\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 111　　年　　 4　  月　  15 　 日\r\n                              書  記  官  彭映婷","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CPEM/111%2c%e7%ab%b9%e5%8c%97%e7%b0%a1%2c162%2c20220810%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CPEM,111,竹北簡,162,20220810,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"竹北簡","JNO":"162","JDATE":"20220810","JTITLE":"恐嚇"}